<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>World Cup 2026 Tracker - Home</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      html {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      body { background: #f9fafb; color: #111827; line-height: 1.5; }
      h1, h2 { line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      a { color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
      button { cursor: pointer; border: none; border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 1rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
      button:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

      .landing-container { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
      .landing-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
      .landing-header h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .landing-header p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; }
      .landing-content { flex: 1; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1rem; width: 100%; }
      .features { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
      .features h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center; }
      .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
      .feature-card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition: transform 0.2s; }
      .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
      .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .feature-card p { color: #6b7280; }
      .cta { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 3rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
      .cta h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
      .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s; }
      .btn-primary { background: #667eea; color: white; }
      .btn-primary:hover { background: #5568d3; }
      .btn-secondary { background: white; color: #667eea; border: 2px solid #667eea; }
      .btn-secondary:hover { background: #667eea; color: white; }
      .info { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
      .info h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .info p { color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .landing-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
        .btn { width: 100%; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="landing-container">
      <header class="landing-header">
        <h1>World Cup 2026 Sticker Tracker</h1>
        <p>Track your Panini FIFA World Cup 2026 album progress</p>
      </header>

      <main class="landing-content">
        <section class="features">
          <h2>Features</h2>
          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <h3>📊 Track Progress</h3>
              <p>Keep track of which stickers you have and which ones you need</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <h3>📈 Statistics</h3>
              <p>View detailed statistics about your collection by country</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <h3>🔍 Search & Filter</h3>
              <p>Find stickers by country, page number, or player name</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <h3>🌐 Open Source API</h3>
              <p>Access complete sticker catalog data for your own projects</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta">
          <h2>Get Started</h2>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login</a>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-secondary">Create Account</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="info">
          <h2>About This Project</h2>
          <p>
            This is an open-source tracker for the FIFA World Cup 2026 Panini sticker album.
            The complete sticker catalog is available via our public API for anyone to use.
          </p>
          <p>
            The album contains 980 stickers across 112 pages, including stickers for all 48 participating teams,
            special FIFA content, and parallel versions.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
